00:12:59.960 --> 00:13:02.200
way, my understanding of the
way Kickstarter works is,

00:13:02.200 --> 00:13:04.050
effectively, this money is sort
of pledged to you ahead

00:13:04.050 --> 00:13:07.250
of time and then you're
kind of given this--

00:13:07.250 --> 00:13:09.090
I'm not sure what the
restrictions are versus the

00:13:09.090 --> 00:13:11.620
lending company to you as an
individual and where the money

00:13:11.620 --> 00:13:14.740
