And then trying to talk to game
developers about hey,

00:16:12.530 --> 00:16:16.760
let's get you on 1,000 units and
get that out to the people

00:16:16.760 --> 00:16:17.340
so you can make money.

00:16:17.340 --> 00:16:18.790
That's a really difficult
discussion.

00:16:18.790 --> 00:16:21.210
TODD KERPELMAN: It does help
solve some of the traction

